    h4#University University College
    p.lead
      | University College was launched in 2005 to systematically promote general and basic education and to support freshmen adjust to university life.
      | University College directs liberal arts education in SKKU and realizes a 21st century learning community by providing academic and university life guidance to freshmen students, before choosing their major.
